    ForwardChecking, Profilable

    public class NFC0
extends AbstractNFC
implements ForwardChecking
    NFC0 is a ForwardChecking implementation for HyperGraph with delayed local propagation.
    delayed: check atoms with only one variable not assigned (after current assignment).
    local: check atoms containing at least one atoms from the set of post variables of the current variable.
    Author:
    Cl√©ment Sipieter (INRIA) <clement@6pi.fr>
